>edge_no_atg Sequence with no ATG start codon
TTTCCCGGGTTTAAACCCTGA
>edge_atg_stop ATG immediately followed by stop codon (6 bases)
ATGTAA
>edge_no_stop ATG with no in-frame stop codon
ATGAAAGGATTTCCCGGG
>edge_overlapping_atg Two ATGs before one stop (maximal ORF uses first ATG)
ATGAAGATGCCCGGATGA
>edge_multiline Sequence split across lines with whitespace
ATG AAA GGA
TTT CCC GGG
TTT AAA CCC TGA
>edge_mixed_case Lowercase sequence that should be normalized
atgaaaggatttcccgggtttaaaccctga
>edge_boundary ORF starting at first nucleotide
ATGAAATGA
